    {
      "id": "sybil_12_listing_1",
      "firm_id": "sybil_12",
      "description": "Hey there! Looking for a reliable ride that\u2019s been really well-loved? I\u2019m parting ways with my trusty car, and it\u2019s in great shape for its next adventure. It runs like a dream and has been super dependable for me. Perfect for daily commutes or weekend getaways! Come take it for a spin\u2014you\u2019ll love how it drives!",
