      "quality_value": 0.1,
      "timestep_posted": 30
    },
    {
      "id": "sybil_6_listing_6",
      "firm_id": "sybil_6",
      "description": "Hey there! I\u2019m parting ways with my trusty ride, and it has been such a joy to drive. It\u2019s in really solid shape\u2014well-loved, clean, and runs like a dream! It's the perfect fit if you're looking for something reliable and ready for the road without the brand-new price tag. I\u2019ve taken great care of it, and I\u2019m sure you\u2019ll love it as much as I have. Drop me a message and let\u2019s get you behind the wheel for a test drive!",
      "price": 29500.0,
